trans-unit.source: Runs multiple instances of a child activity.
trans-unit.target: Kör flera instanser av en underordnad aktivitet.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] The ReplicatorActivity is similar to a `for each` statement in code.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]ReplicatorActivity liknar en `for each` kodrad.

trans-unit.source: If you are presented with a task in which you repeat the same function on many different entities, ReplicatorActivity may be a better solution than <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WhileActivity>.
trans-unit.target: Om du får med en aktivitet som du upprepa samma funktion på många olika enheter, ReplicatorActivity kan det vara bättre än <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WhileActivity>.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WhileActivity>

trans-unit.source: By default, a ReplicatorActivity is completed when all child instances have completed.
trans-unit.target: Som standard har en ReplicatorActivity slutförts när alla underordnade instanser har slutförts.

trans-unit.source: You can override this behavior with a custom condition to use when the activity finishes.
trans-unit.target: Du kan åsidosätta detta beteende med ett anpassat villkor som ska användas när aktiviteten har slutförts.

trans-unit.source: If this condition evaluates to `true` before all child instances have completed, then any running incomplete child instances are canceled.
trans-unit.target: Om det här villkoret utvärderas till `true` före alla underordnade instanser har slutförts och sedan alla körs ofullständiga underordnade instanser har avbrutits.

trans-unit.source: If subscribed to, this event is raised every time that an instance of the child activity is created for an item in the `Children` collection.
trans-unit.target: Om du prenumererar på denna händelse utlöses varje gång som en instans av den underordnade aktiviteten har skapats för ett objekt i den `Children` samling.

trans-unit.source: The `Children` collection is set through the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorChildEventArgs> of the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity.Initialized> event handler.
trans-unit.target: Den `Children` samling anges via den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorChildEventArgs>av den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity.Initialized>händelsehanteraren.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity.Initialized> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorChildEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The child <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> instance is passed in the call so that the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity> can set values on the child.
trans-unit.target: Underordnat <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>förekomst skickas i anropet så att den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity>kan ange värden på underordnade.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>

trans-unit.source: The relevant <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorChildEventArgs.InstanceData%2A> object from the `Children` collection is also passed.
trans-unit.target: Relevant <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorChildEventArgs.InstanceData%2A>objekt från den `Children` samling skickas också.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorChildEventArgs.InstanceData%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets an array of running child activity instances.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en matris med-aktivitetsinstanser som körs underordnad.

trans-unit.source: The activity instances returned by this property are the instances of the activity type that are contained within the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity>.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitetsinstanser som returneras av den här egenskapen är instanser av aktivitetstypen som ingår i <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity>.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity> is running in sequence mode, the array contains no more than one activity; if running in parallel mode the array contains all instances that are currently running.
trans-unit.target: Om den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity>körs i sekvens läge matrisen innehåller mer än en aktivitet; om körs i Parallelläge matrisen innehåller alla instanser som körs för närvarande.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a completion condition that indicates when the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity"></xref> should finish.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett villkor för slutförande som anger när den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity"> </xref> ska slutföras.

trans-unit.source: This default condition is that all child instances must complete for the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity> to be completed.
trans-unit.target: Det här villkoret för standard är att alla underordnade instanser måste slutföra för den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity>ska slutföras.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ReplicatorActivity>

trans-unit.source: As with a <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ConditionedActivityGroup>, you can specify the completion condition using a rule condition or code condition.
trans-unit.target: Precis som med en <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ConditionedActivityGroup>, du kan ange villkoret slutfördes med ett regelvillkor eller Kodvillkor.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ConditionedActivityGroup>
